headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Expedia Group (EXPE) After Its 57% One-Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Expedia Group’s share price still reflects good value after a strong run, you are not alone. This article is built to help you frame that question clearly. The stock last closed at US$290.76, with returns of 2.6% over 30 days and 57.1% over the past year. These returns can shift how the market views both its growth potential and its risk.
